citation.case_name: City of New Orleans v. United States Ex Rel. Christmas Same v. Same

html:
131 U.S. 220

9 S.Ct. 755

33 L.Ed. 110

CITY OF NEW ORLEANS
v.
UNITED STATES ex rel. CHRISTMAS et al.
SAME
v.
SAME.

May 13, 1889.

BRADLEY, J.

1

The decision just made in the case of City of New Orleans v. Myra Clark Gaines, ante, 745, renders it necessary that the judgment or decree in this case should be reversed, and it is reversed accordingly, and the cause remanded, with instructions to dismiss the petition.
